Title: Supersymmetric penguin contributions to the process
  \protect\protect\protect(B_{d}\longrightarrow \Phi K_{s}\protect \protect
  \protect) in SUSY GUT with right-handed neutrino.} Abstract: The (B_{d}\longrightarrow \Phi K_{s}) process is without tree level decay
amplitude . Then the SUSY contributions may be significant . We calculate the
neutralino and gluino penguin contributions to the CP violating phase in (SU(5)
) grand unified theory with right-handed neutrino (SU(5)_{RN}) . We find that
the SUSY contribution may change the phase in (B_{d}\longrightarrow \Phi K_{s}
).
